    <title type="html"><![CDATA[SCSS小技巧：更結構化的寫margin、padding、font..etc]]></title>
    <link href="http://hechien.github.com/octopress/blog/scssxiao-ji-qiao-%3Ageng-jie-gou-hua-de-xie-margin%2C-padding%2C-font-dot-etc/"/>
